description:
Someone said I have to be like Daruma.
Fall and get up.
No matter how many times to fall, It can get up.

Please stop think so.
Get up because want to get up and get up because must get up, It's different.

Whether want to get up or not, Daruma has to get up.
No matter how much want to fall, Daruma will never fall.

Why push to see me always get up?

When will I fall?

It hurts so much.

A N Y O N E P L E A S E S T O P M E

I'm tired of getting up.
